{"tid":2283974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：疫情反彈似第三波之初　料與放寬社交措施有關","createTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T10:00:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"20b989173fac96f6e3c66eb0e198cf31302b4b13","tid":2283974,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指，近日疫情反彈趨勢似第三波爆發之初，要密切留意發展；又指感染數字增加，是社交距離措施放寬的代價。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌：「看到第三波早期亦都一樣，數字突然單位變雙位，接著很快高雙位變三位，源頭不明比例又會高，以及在不同地區出現。這幾天真的令人擔心，看似可能會發生。近期措施放寬了，多了人外出消費，這是其中一個代價，各地政府都是一放寬措施，市民就會多參加社交活動，風險就會提高。」<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌又指，若的士司機感染個案持續增加，有需要考慮要求他們接受強制檢測。對於近日幼稚園爆發上呼吸道感染，他就指，情況與以往相近，幼童個人衞生不及成年人，會是最先受感染的群組。"},{"pid":"607fa84e225efdf390f68c61fe64af5d5a9dee2e","tid":2283974,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=412716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412716&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BykzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=94c0d20f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412716&h=437ad2b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=412716</a>"},{"pid":"6bf465dff6ad7c37712c3a652b0dc8849257d0cc","tid":2283974,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"叫雞群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc82e9efc2d5ce6dc2e8b75f260541198db583ac","tid":2283974,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"永瀆 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f515adb54ae01105b7fbbf6180f5b2bb475edba","tid":2283974,"uid":136797,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"班專家正一死毒撚<br /